Package: microclCorr
Title: Machine Learning Correction of Microclimate Model Predictions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Gilad", "Mazor", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "gilad.mazor@mail.huji.ac.il"),
    person("Ofir", "Levy", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides functions to train Random Forest and LSTM models
    that correct systematic biases in physical microclimate model predictions
    (e.g. NicheMapR) using temperature logger measurements. Supports data
    alignment, feature engineering, model training with optional hyperparameter
    tuning, and prediction correction across multiple habitats and spatial scales.
